  <summary date="2021-06-11T14:23:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Plasma Donation Awareness Act of 2020

This bill includes plasma donation within the scope of a public awareness campaign by the Department of Health and Human Services concerning the importance of the blood supply and the need for blood donations during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) emergency.</summary>
